detail.title: FindTruman — Create a STEAM-like Story-gameplay Co-creation Platform in Web3
detail.description:
# Background and Motivation

Story-gameplay (also known as Script-Murder) is becoming popular in recent years. Based on the story, the player acts as one of the story roles, and interacts with others to achieve the ultimate goal from the first perspective. It is characterized by the strong immersion, content-based, social networking attributes, etc.

Our team started story-gameplay Web2 project from 2017 and became one of the TOP brands. We have accumulated 30 million Web2 users, nearly 100 offline studios which can enjoy offline story-gameplay services in different cities.

With the rapid growing, this industry encounters some issues which need to be solved urgently, for example:
* Piracy is rampant;
* Creators only get a small part of the story selling;
* Players have no way to be profitable;
* Creation effeciency is low;

These issues limit the development of the whole industry. We found that Web3 and AIGC are very suitable to solve the problems and can give an explosive growth for the production of high-quality contents. 

# What do we build?

Our vision is to create a STEAM-like story-gameplay co-creation platform with Web3 and AIGC technologies. To solve the current issues above, we designed the FindTruman platform containing UGC editor platform and story-gameplay platform.

## UGC(User-Generated Content) editor platform

UGC editor platform is a multi-chain co-creation platform. With our designed multi-chain mechanism, the creators will freely publish the stories to corresponding blockchain according to the communities they want to attract. It can attract more participants and strengthen the fluidity of the Story-NFT and story content.

1) Story content on chain
The creators can freely create their stories, and update the stories according to the feedbacks. All the story contents will be recorded on chain.

2) Issue Story-NFT
The creator could issue Story-NFT on the corresponding chain according to the communities they want to attract. 

3) Co-creation with Story-NFT
The creators could set the co-creation tasks, like creation of the story imags, translation, 3D construction, etc., and incentivize others with Story-NFT to join the co-creation procedure together.

4) AIGC (Artificial Intelligence Generated Content) tools
With AI technology, our platform will assist the creators to expand the inspiration of story creation, automatically improve the story logic and polish the story, intelligently generate story covers and illustrations. It will lower the threshold for content creation and empower more users to quickly create high-quality contents with AIGC technologies.

At the end of this procedure, the story will have high quality contents or IP with their first fans. UGC editor platform is aimed to improve the creation efficiency, e.g. creators’ creation periods will reduce greatly from 8 weeks to 2 weeks.

## Story-gameplay platform

1) Construct 3D story-gameplay
For the completed stories on UGC editor, the users or community fans could build the releated 3D scenes by dragging and dropping on the page, just like Decentraland, Sandbox, etc. Then, 3D story-gameplay will be released on the story-gameplay platform for public to experience.

2) Enjoy the unprecedented gaming experience
For Web2 and Web3 players, they will pay the tickets to be immersed in 3D story-gameplays. In the story-gameplays, the players need to act as one of the story roles and interact with other players to unlock the hidden clues. Finally, they will make reasoning to reveal the truth. It will bring the players unprecedented gaming experience through the strong sense of immersion, various story contents and social networking. 

3) Obtain incentives
Players need to pay for the tickets of story-gameplay, and they could get further rewards if they have an excellent performance. 


# Our differentials

1) TOP brand of story-gameplay category
Our team started story-gameplay Web2 project from 2017 and became one of the TOP brands in this category.

2) Accumulation of large user group base
We have accumulated more than 30 million Web2 online users and 1,500 creators.

3) Multi-chain integration
Our story-gameplay platform and UGC editor platform both support the integration of multi-chains. Creators from other ecosystems can easily join in building IRISnet after the integration. We have supported several chains, including Polygon, Ethereum, NEAR, Dfinity, etc. In the future, we are looking forward to the cross-chain transfer of assets between IRIS and other chains. This will allow users to easily transfer the digital assets. In this way, the liquidity and value of NFTs will be increased. Moreover, it will also allow users on different blockchains to share resources and information. It will drive the collaboration and development of blockchains. Finally, a wider community and network will be built.


# Our previous works

1) We have constucted the initial version of UGC editor platform with multi-chains. It can provide more choices and flexibility. The users will be allowed to choose the blockchain that suits their needs and preferences,access more blockchain ecos and discover more value and potential. Currently, our platform has successfully integrated with Polygon, NEAR, Ethereum, Dfinity, Tezos, and etc. Here is the demo video of UGC editor: https://youtu.be/yjrb5hYAcJU 

2) We have construct the demo of story-gameplay platform (https://youtu.be/-TApcp99avQ) 

3) We have built the early community of our project in Web3. We have successfully attracted nearly 20K followers in our Twitter, 14K followers in our Discord and 25K participation badges. 

4) We have won several international hackathons, including: 
* Champion of 2022 Wanxiang blockchain hackathon
* 3rd place of Polygon’s global hackathon
* Bronze winner of ABGA blockchain gaming hackathon.


# What and how would our project improve the IRISnet ecosystem?

1) Our project focus on the multi-chain NFT gaming. Through integrating with IRISnet, users could issue the story contents and Story-NFT on IRISnet. In future, we will realize the cross-chain transfer of assets through IRIS protocol. The liquidity and value of NFTs will be enhanced, and it will drive the collaboration and development of blockchains.

2) Introduce players from our Web2 platform. Our team started story-gameplay Web2 project from 2017 and became one of the TOP brands in this category. We will attract users from Web2 by our incentive mechanisms and promotions to IRISnet and Cosmos ecosystem.

3) We will build the story-gameplay with the theme of IRISnet to attract more creators and players to participate in the co-creation procedure, which will have a better promotion effect of IRISnet. 


# What is the detailed work plan?

1) Develop the story releasing functions of UGC editor integrating IRISnet. The creators can freely release and update their own stories on chain. Moreover, we will develop the function of Story-NFT on IRISnet. 

2) Develop the co-creation functions of UGC editor integrating IRISnet. The creators could set the co-creation tasks and incentivize others to join the co-creation procedures with the rewards of Story-NFT on IRISnet.

3) Based on the UGC editor platform, we will build a new 3D story scene story-gameplay and launch on IRISnet. The story-gameplay will be opened to the public to experience and play. We will co-host the story-gameplay with IRISnet ecosystem.

4) Develop an AIGC(AI Generated Content) tool with text-to-image function. It will help creators on IRISnet to generate wonderful contents just by inputting text, which will make their stories more vivid. Host story competition with blue-chip communities.

5) Improve AIGC tool with Text-to-Music & Text-to-3D functions, which could intelligently help creators on IRISnet to generate 3D models and music contents. It will generate various 3D models to the story-gameplays.


# What kind of resources are being requested?

We need some fund to support the partial cost of the hardware resource and the labor cost of our developers, and contribute to the innovation and prosperity of IRISnet. Here are our milestones and deliverables:

**[Milestone 1]**
Duration: 6 weeks
Funds request: 12,000 USD
Deliverables:
* Design UI/UX of story releasing functions.
* Develop the function of issuing story content on IRISnet. The creators can freely release their own stories, and update their stories according to readers’ feedbacks.
* Develop the function of Story-NFT on IRISnet. The creator could specify the related NFT information and issue the Story-NFT on IRISnet.

**[Milestone 2]**
Duration: 4 weeks
Funds request: 7,000 USD
Deliverables:
* Design UI/UX of co-creation functions.
* Develop the co-creation functions. The creators could set the co-creation tasks, like translation, image design or 3D construction, and incentivize others to join the co-creation process with the rewards of Story-NFT on IRISnet. The user of the best work will be rewarded as the corresponding NFT after the creator’s review. 
* Gather ideas based on users’ feedback

**[Milestone 3]**
Duration: 4 weeks
Funds request: 6,000 USD
Deliverables:
* Design UI/UX of 3D scene story-gameplay.
* Develop the customized 3D scene story-gameplay for IRISnet. 
* The story-gameplay will be opened to the IRISnet network members to experience and play. Collaborate with other projects in IRISnet, e.g. co-host AMA, games and other events.

In future, we are looking forward to the cross-chain transfer of assets between IRIS and other chains. This will allow users to easily transfer the digital assets, which will increase the liquidity and value of NFTs, allowing developers and users on different blockchains to share resources and information, building a wider community and network.

HashKey DID is a multi-chain decentralised identity data aggregator powered by smart contract, NFT, and privacy protection decentralized protocol to provide identity services to Web3 users. detail.title: Parameter Change: Increase Deposit Amount for IRISnet Governance
detail.description:
## [Proposal] Parameter Change: Increase Deposit Amount for IRISnet Governance

To deter spam governance proposals containing malicious links that can harm the unaware IRISnet community, and encourage thoughtful proposal submissions, we propose raising the current deposit amount (which is a subtle cost for spamming) for IRISnet governance.

By the time of writing and at the current token price value, the minimum deposit costs  **1,000 IRIS** (approximately **30 USD**equivalent) , which appears to be insufficient for preventing spam and marketing proposals.

The minimum deposit will be raised to **5,000 IRIS** if this proposal is approved (approximately **150 USD** equivalent). This change is not permanent and can be reversed at any time through governance.

## Voting

* By voting YES, you agree that the minimum deposit for a proposal to enter the voting period should be increased from 1,000 IRIS to 5,000 IRIS.
* By voting NO, you disagree in part or in entirety with one or more of the above statements.
* By voting ABSTAIN, you formally decline to vote either for or against the proposal.
* By voting NOWITHVETO, you seek to penalize the proposal depositors by burning their deposit, and contribute towards an automatic 1/3 veto threshold, which would result in proposal failure if reached.

# Make IRISnet the Sponsor of the Game of NFTs Phase 2 Hackathon

## Summary

This proposal is requesting 1,490,758 IRIS (Approximately USD $50k) from the IRISnet Community Pool to make IRISnet the sponsor of the Game of NFTs and cover the prizes of the GoN Phase 2 Hackathon IRISnet challenge.

## Details

This is a community spend proposal to fund the prizes of the IRISnet challenge that are part of the upcoming Game of NFTs Phase 2 Hackathon. This will be able to bring talented NFT projects into the IRISnet ecosystem and benefits our community, which is aligned with our mission to become the Interchain NFT Hub.

We are requesting 1,490,758 IRIS that will be sent to a multisig maintained by a committee that consists of:

* Harvey | IRISnet
* Jeffrey Hu | HashKey Capital
* Brian Xin | Uptick

Note that the judges will award prizes only in case the submissions are of high quality and meet all the criteria outlined in the challenge, and any surplus will be returned to the Community Pool.

The full text of the proposal with all details can be found at [https://forum.irisnet.org/t/draft-proposal-23-make-irisnet-the-sponsor-of-game-of-nfts-phase-2-hackathon/749](https://forum.irisnet.org/t/draft-proposal-23-make-irisnet-the-sponsor-of-game-of-nfts-phase-2-hackathon/749)

## Vote

* YES - You approve of funding 1,490,758 IRIS to the Prize Pool of the GoN Phase 2 Hackathon.
* NO - You reject this funding request.
* NO WITH VETO - You believe that this proposal is not beneficial to the Network.
* ABSTAIN - You wish to contribute to the quorum but you decline to vote either for or against the proposal.

This is the way to make Uptick on IRISnet maintain it as the important COSMOS native NFT marketplace and grow with the market in 2023. We believe this major upgrade will strengthen the NFT hub position of IRISnet in the wider Cosmos ecosystem and IRISnet-WenChang interchain ecosystem, and also bring more value and usage to IRISnet’s platform token. If the proposal is passed, we will invest 3 months to carry out the overall transformation and the Uptick Marketplace on IRISnet 2.0 will be officially launched on 31st March, 2023. detail.description: IRISnet will create IOV/IRIS liquidity pool and its corresponding farming pool on CoinSwap, to bring more liquidity to both IRISnet and Starname ecosystem. detail.title: Support IRISnet-resided IBC Tokens in Uptick Marketplace
detail.description: Uptick Marketplace on IRISnet is the NFT Marketplace with the longest operating time, the largest number of high-quality NFT assets and the highest user participation in the COSMOS ecosystem. In order to further promote the operation of this Marketplace on IRISnet, further activate the community of IRISnet and practically connect to and unite other IBC chain's community, especially the ATOM community, we planned to add support to several tokens in Uptick Marketplace through IBC in Q3. If it goes well, it will bring positive value for IRISnet, COSMOS, Coinswap, and Uptick Marketplace. The specific implementation is as follows: 1.Implement the support of IBC assets for a variety of COSMOS ecological tokens deposit to IRISnet through IBC in the IRISnet-based Uptick Marketplace (both web and mobile app versions), such as ATOM and others via IBC. 2.Uptick users can select these deposited tokens on IRISnet for pricing and purchasing. This makes Uptick Marketplace support multiple tokens and can cover multiple token communities. 3.Establish bonus pool of the corresponding IBC token to reward users who use these tokens for NFT transactions. 4. Within 1 month after the launch, special claimable rewards will be given to community users who participate in the activities through this channel. Planning and implementation period: Now-2022.8.15. Target release time: 2022.8.15, Market campaign and operation with incentive phase: 2022.8.15-2022.9.30.

detail.description:
In order to improve the governance efficiency and bring more events frequently in the decentralized manner, this proposal requests approval to reduce the on-chain governance voting period to 5 days. 
With the active support and participation of validators and delegators, the previous proposals achieved quorum in about 3 days; therefore, after evaluation, we propose that shortening the voting period to 5 days will allow sufficient time for discussion, evaluation, and voting, while also being more in line with our rapid pace in terms of upgrades, events, and more.

detail.title: Increase MaxValidators to 108
detail.description:
This proposal is about increasing the Maximum Number of Validators on IRIS Hub. Once this proposal passes, the number of active validators on the IRIS Hub mainnet will be increased from 100 to 108, which gives more validators the opportunity to participate in contributing to the network security, further boosting the constant expansion of IRISnet ecosystem.
 In the Cosmos ecosystem, IRIS Hub is virtually one of the few mainnets where the active validator always reaches the maximum number. Currently, there are 100 active validators on IRIS Hub mainnet. And this proposal intends to increase the maximum number so that there will be more validators allowed to join IRISnet ecosystem and then better support the network decentralization.

detail.title: Enable IBC transfers
detail.description:
The Proposal enables transferring and receiving assets using the ICS20 standard on the IRIS Hub. If this proposal passes, there will be IBC assets available in the Bank module of the IRIS Hub and IRIS token will be available on Zones connected over IBC. And the other assets on the IRIS Hub such as native issued tokens, HTLT tokens, LP tokens will all be able to transfer to the other Hubs or Zones. With IBC transfer enabled, there will be more liquidity to the IRIS Hub and the Coinswap module.
 Please note that IBC transfer can only be enabled after the proposal 1 passed and irishub upgraded to v1.1.0 (https://irishub.iobscan.io/#/ProposalsDetail/1), because there is a known security vulnerability identified by IRISnet team and fixed in the cosmos-sdk v0.42.3.
